gw.api.json

Class JsonConfigAccess

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.json.JsonConfigAccess

  • public class JsonConfigAccess
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides static methods for accessing JsonMappings, JsonSchemas, and mapping Filters.

    • Method Summary

      • getMapping

        public static JsonMapping getMapping(java.lang.String name)
        Retrieves the named JsonMapping, or throws an exception if the name is malformed or there's no JsonMapping with that name
        Parameters:
        name - the fully-qualified name of the mapping, including the version
        Returns:
        the JsonMapping with that name

      • getMapper

        public static JsonMapper getMapper(java.lang.String mappingName,
                                   java.lang.String mapperName)
        Retrieves the named JsonMapper from the named JsonMapping. This method will throw an exception if the mapping name is malformed or there is no JsonMapping with that name.
        Parameters:
        mappingName - the fully-qualified name of the mapping, including the version
        mapperName - the name of the mapper within that mapping
        Returns:
        the JsonMapper from that mapping, or null if that mapping has no JsonMapper with that name

      • getSchema

        public static JsonSchema getSchema(java.lang.String name)
        Retrieves the named JsonSchema, or throws an exception if the name is malformed or there's no JsonSchema with that name
        Parameters:
        name - the fully-qualified name of the schema, including the version
        Returns:
        the JsonSchema with that name

      • getSchemaDefinition

        public static JsonSchemaDefinition getSchemaDefinition(java.lang.String schemaName,
                                                       java.lang.String definitionName)
        Retrieves the named JsonSchemaDefinition from the named JsonSchema. This method will throw an exception if the schema name is malformed or there is no JsonSchema with that name.
        Parameters:
        schemaName - the fully-qualified name of the schema, including the version
        definitionName - the name of the definition within that schema
        Returns:
        the JsonSchemaDefinition from that schema, or null if that schema has no definition with that name

      • getFilter

        Returns:
